[Chapter Select]
author=bungholio
description=Found with PS2rd. Use it with a joker command. I didn&#039;t test it much, but the few chapters that I did try worked just fine, unlock in Fatal Frame 3 where 2 of them messed up a little. There are 10 chapters. &quot;9&quot; is the last chapter in Hard or Nightmare Mode, and &quot;A&quot; is some extra chapter that I didn&#039;t check at all. I don&#039;t know if it is part of one chapter or just a copy or slightly different version of another chapter.
patch=1,EE,002BCF50,extended,0000000A

