author=bungholio
description=FFFFFFFF - On
00000000 - Off
patch=1,EE,202E1050,extended,FFFFFFFF

[Freeze Certain Ghosts (R2 + Up freeze, R2 + Down unfreeze)]
author=bungholio
description=002a2cc3 00000040 and 002a2cc3 00000080 also freeze the same ghosts. If you take a picture of a ghost it will start moving again. It doesn&#039;t always stop them right away, they usually go to the end of an animation and stop which is even better so it&#039;s easier to get fatal frame shots. But it didn&#039;t seem to affect all ghosts. I used it on the drowned woman, and that female ghost that you defeated at the end of chapter 1, and the mourners. It didn&#039;t work on veiled priests or kusabi though, so it doesn&#039;t work on all ghosts.
patch=1,EE,D02BB682,extended,0000FDEF
patch=1,EE,002A2CC4,extended,00000001
patch=1,EE,D02BB682,extended,0000FDBF
patch=1,EE,002A2CC4,extended,00000000

