[Unlock Accessories]
author=bungholio
description=02 - Mio Accessory
04 - Mayu Accessory
06 - Both Accessories

NOTE - If your cheat device is old and doesn&#039;t have that OR code type, change the first 7 to a 2.

You need to beat the game at least once and save it to get the menu that allows you to use these.
patch=1,EE,A02E637D,extended,86803A68

[Unlock Completed Game Menu]
author=bungholio
description=Found with PS2rd. Just load any game to use it. It saves.
patch=1,EE,002BCF52,extended,00000001

[Unlock Costumes]
author=bungholio
description=0002 - A
0004 - B
0008 - C
0010 - D
0020 - E
0040 - F
0080 - G
0100 - H
01ff - All Costumes Unlocked

NOTE - If your cheat device is old and doesn&#039;t have that OR code type, change the first 7 to a 2.

You need to beat the game at least once and save it to get the menu that allows you to use these.
patch=1,EE,00CE51A5,extended,00000011

[Unlock Difficulty]
author=bungholio
description=01 - Easy
02 - Normal
04 - Hard
08 - Nightmare
0f - All Difficulties Unlocked

NOTE - If your cheat device is old and doesn&#039;t have that OR code type, change the first 7 to a 2.

You need to beat the game at least once and save it to get the menu that allows you to use these.
patch=1,EE,C03779DC,extended,D9942AF6

[Unlock Ending Codes]
author=bungholio
description=01 - normal ending only (Crimson Butterfly)
02 - hard ending only (Hellish Abyss)
03 - both normal and hard endings

NOTE - If your cheat device is old and doesn&#039;t have that OR code type, change the first 7 to a 2.
patch=1,EE,8134DDF4,extended,C67BF731

