[Visual Filters]
author=bungholio
description=0 = Off
1, 2, 3, 4, 5 = Different Filters
Found with PS2rd. It has slightly different visual effects, including that noise filter effect the game has at moments when ghosts appear. Do not use &quot;06&quot; or higher, it will freeze the game.
